      • merchantId

        private Optional<String> merchantId
        This parameter is for facilitating testing. The scenario is when you set up different Netaxept test accounts for different test purposes. This parameter gives control as to which account to use. It is used as key for selecting correct set of Netaxept credentials. If not present default parameters are used.
